<paragraph blockId="3.[136,1459,485,1792]" box="[189,1251,1594,1619]" pageId="3" pageNumber="383">Relation to host. The mites are vagrants on the undersurfaces of the leaves, with no visible damage.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[136,1459,485,1792]" box="[189,522,1629,1653]" pageId="3" pageNumber="383">
